text: Jan Mościcki (born February 6, 1988 in Łódź, Poland) is a Polish ice dancer. With former partner Joanna Budner, he is a three-time (2007–2009) Polish national champion. Their partnership ended following the 2008-2009 season. He teamed up with Anastasia Vykhodtseva in 2009.
